ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectSpekne'katik and Millbrook First Nation Halifax County 1919 Invalid Surrender Specific Claim Settlement Agreement
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations to enter into and execute, on behalf of Her Majesty the Queen in right of Canada, the SIPEKNE'KATIK AND MILLBROOK FIRST NATION HALIFAX COUNTRY 1919 INVALID SURRENDER SPECIFIC CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the Sipekne'katik and Millbrook First Nation; and (2) accepting the instrument which absolutely surrenders to Canada of all rights and interests in the Surrendered Lands.
